<script type="text/javascript">
    function check(day) {
        var showCheck = $('.posRmenu a').attr('class');
        if (showCheck == 'toogleBtn show') {
            createCookie('widgetCheck', 'false', day);
        }
        else {
            createCookie('widgetCheck', 'true', day);
        }
    }

    function getCookie(c_name) {
        var i, x, y, EachCookies = document.cookie.split(";");
        for (i = 0; i < EachCookies.length; i++) {
            x = EachCookies[i].substr(0, EachCookies[i].indexOf("="));
            //x為key
            y = EachCookies[i].substr(EachCookies[i].indexOf("=") + 1);
            //y為value
            x = x.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, "");
            //g:找到所有符合的字串
            //^：以甚麼開始的字串
            //\s：空白字元
            //+：前面的字元有一至多個
            //$：以前一個字元為結尾的字串
            //(以空白為開頭的一個或多個空白字元)或(一個或多個空白最後以空白結尾的字元)
            //去掉前後的空白
            if (x == c_name) {
                return unescape(y);
                //利用unescape()解碼在網路上傳遞的字串
                //需要在網路上傳遞的字串應該以escape()予以編碼
            }
        }
    }

    function createCookie(name, value, days) {
        if (days) {
            var date = new Date();
            date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
            var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
        }
        else {
            var expires = "";
        }
        document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
    }

    $(document).ready(function () {
        var widgetCookie = getCookie('widgetCheck');
        if (widgetCookie === undefined) {
            setCookie('widgetCheck', 'true', 90);
        $('.toogleBtn').addClass('show');
        $('.tooglePage').addClass('show');
        $('.posRmenu').stop().animate({ width: 120 })
        $('.tooglePage').stop().slideDown();
    }
    else {
        if (widgetCookie == 'true') {
            $('.toogleBtn').addClass('show');
            $('.tooglePage').addClass('show');
            $('.posRmenu').stop().animate({ width: 120 })
            $('.tooglePage').stop().slideDown();
        }
        else if (widgetCookie == 'false') {
            $('.toogleBtn').removeClass('show');
            $('.tooglePage').removeClass('show');
            $('.posRmenu').stop().animate({ width: 50 })
            $('.tooglePage').stop().slideUp();
        }
    }
    });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">

    detailTab_add_active(0);

    $(document).ready(function () {

        var pikadayfield1 = document.getElementById('TxtDatepicker');
        var pikadaytrigger1 = document.getElementById('datepicker1-button');
        var txt_deposit1 = document.getElementById('Txt_deposit1');

        //time
        function timeDataBindRateQuoteTime(day, item) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "/bank/Layouts/esunbank/Deposit/DpService.aspx/GetRateQuoteTime",
                contentType: 'application/json; charset=utf-8',
                dataType: 'json',
                async: false,
                cache: false,
                data: "{day:'" + day + "',time:'" + item.value + "',rateType:'ASLL'}",
                success: function (msg) {

                    var result = $.parseJSON(msg.d);
                    $('.timerSelect > li', '#tab-01').remove();
                    var firstTime = '';
                    $.each(result, function (index, value) {
                        $(".timer ul", '#tab-01').append('<li>' + value + '</li>');
                        firstTime = firstTime == '' ? value : firstTime;
                    });

                    //調整高度
                    settingHeight(result, $('.timer .timerSelect', '#tab-01'));

                    $('.timerSelect > li', '#tab-01').on('click', function () {
                        var getTime = $(this).text();
                        $(this).parents('.greyblock').children('.timeInput').val(getTime);
                        $(this).parent().hide();
                        rateDataBindForeignExchage(day, item);
                    });
                    $(item).val(firstTime);
                    rateDataBindForeignExchage(day, item);
                }
            });
        }

        //data
        function rateDataBindForeignExchage(day, item) {
            var context = '#LbQuoteTime';
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "/bank/Layouts/esunbank/Deposit/DpService.aspx/GetForeignExchageRate",
                contentType: 'application/json; charset=utf-8',
                dataType: 'json',
                async: false,
                cache: false,
                data: "{day:'" + day + "',time:'" + item.value + "'}",
                success: function (msg) {
                    var result = $.parseJSON(msg.d);
                    var jsonData = result.Rates;
                    var quoteTime = result.QuoteTime;
                    tableDataBind(jsonData);
                    $(context).text(quoteTime);
                }
            });
        }

        //render
        function tableDataBind(result) {

            $("#inteTable1 tr").not(".titleRow").remove();

            $.each(result, function (index, item) {
                tresult = '<tr class="tableContent-light" align="center">';
                tresult += '<td data-name="外幣類型" class="itemTtitle"> <img src="' + item.Url + '" border="0" width="23" height="15"><a href="/bank/personal/deposit/rate/forex/exchange-rate-chart?Currency=' + item.CCY + '">' + item.Title + '<img class="rc" src="/bank/images/esunbank/deposit/icon_rc.png" alt="走勢圖"></a></td>';
                tresult += '<td data-name="即期買入匯率"  class="odd">' + item.BBoardRate + '</td>';
                tresult += '<td data-name="即期賣出匯率"  class="even">' + item.SBoardRate + '</td>';
                tresult += '<td data-name="現金買入匯率"  class="odd">' + item.CashBBoardRate + '</td>';
                tresult += '<td data-name="現金賣出匯率"  class="even lastTd">' + item.CashSBoardRate + '</td>';
                tresult += '</tr>';
                $("#inteTable1").append(tresult);
            });
        }

        $('.timer > img', '#tab-01').on('click', function () {
            $(this).siblings('.timerSelect').show();
        })

        $('.timerSelect > li', '#tab-01').on('click', function () {
            var getTime = $(this).text();
            $(this).parents('.greyblock').children('.timeInput').val(getTime);
            $(this).parent().hide();
        })

        $('.timer', '#tab-01').click(function () {
            $(document).unbind().bind('click', close1);
        })

        $(pikadayfield1).unbind("change").bind("change", function () {
            timeDataBindRateQuoteTime(pikadayfield1.value, txt_deposit1);
        });

        //日期選擇 1
        new Pikaday(
        {
            field: pikadayfield1,
            trigger: pikadaytrigger1,
            minDate: getServerTime('2017-11-15'),
            maxDate: getServerTime('2017-11-17'),
            yearRange: getYearRange(3),
            customDay: eval('[15,16,17]')
        });
    });

</script>

<a class="btns bigBtn mt10 fancybox ml10" id="triggerMessagePopup" style="display: none;" href="#messagePopup"></a>
<script type="text/javascript">
    //還原預設值
    function ResetMsgArgs() {
        window.MsgPopupArgs = { 'msg': '請傳入訊息!', 'usehtml': true, 'title': '訊息', 'closetext': '確認' };
    }
    //變更欄位值
    function ChangeMsgField(field, value, args) {
        if (value != undefined) {
            if (value != '') {
                eval('args.' + field + ' = "' + value + '";');
            } else if (value == false) {
                eval('args.' + field + ' = Boolean(' + value + ');');
            }
        }
    }
    //純文字顯示訊息 msg:訊息 title:標題 closetext:關閉按鍵顯示文字
    function messagePopup(msg, title, closetext, usehtml) {
        ResetMsgArgs();
        ChangeMsgField('title', title, window.MsgPopupArgs);
        ChangeMsgField('closetext', closetext, window.MsgPopupArgs);
        ChangeMsgField('msg', msg, window.MsgPopupArgs);
        ChangeMsgField('usehtml', usehtml, window.MsgPopupArgs);
        messagePopupInternal(window.MsgPopupArgs);
    }

    function messagePopupInternal(args) {
        $('div#messagePopup h2.head').text(args.title);
        var content = window.messageContent != undefined ? window.messageContent : args.msg;
        window.messageContent = undefined;
        if (args.usehtml)
            $('div#messagePopup div#popupContent p').html(content);
        else
            $('div#messagePopup div#popupContent p').text(content);
        $('div#messagePopup a.close').text(args.closetext);
        $('#triggerMessagePopup').trigger('click');
    }
</script>
